article.headline: Chebuhar scores 20 as Lehigh takes down Holy Cross 78-72
article.description: — Burke Chebuhar scored 20 points as Lehigh beat Holy Cross 78-72 on Saturday.
article.linkText: Chebuhar scores 20 as Lehigh takes down Holy Cross 78-72
article.story: WORCESTER, Mass. -- — Burke Chebuhar scored 20 points as Lehigh beat Holy Cross 78-72 on Saturday. Chebuhar added 10 rebounds for the Mountain Hawks (6-13, 3-5 Patriot League). Tyler Whitney-Sidney scored 19 points, going 7 of 13 from the floor, including 2 for 6 from 3-point range, and 3 for 8 from the line. Joshua Ingram shot 5 for 9, including 3 for 5 from beyond the arc to finish with 14 points. Joseph Octave led the Crusaders (5-16, 2-6) in scoring, finishing with 20 points, six rebounds and three steals. Caleb Kenney added 14 points, six rebounds and two steals for Holy Cross. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
